item.title: 10th Feb: The Recall (2017), 1hr 30m [R] (5.25/10)
item.description: A getaway trip to a country lake becomes a fight for survival when five friends realize that an alien invasion and mass abduction are underway.

item.title: 10th Feb: Love for Sale 2 (2019), 1hr 35m [TV-14] (6/10)
item.description: Exhausted with his mother's failed attempts at setting him up with women, Ican hires an ideal partner from a matchmaking app.

item.title: 9th Feb: Fronteras (2018), 1hr 45m [TV-MA] (5.15/10)
item.description: When a new, deadly narcotic sweeps the American Southwest, a Border Patrol agent must contend with a task force that challenges his duties and morals.

item.description: A teen's discovery of a vintage Polaroid camera develops into a darker tale when she finds that whoever takes their photo with it dies soon afterward.

item.title: 8th Feb: The Coldest Game (2019), 1hr 43m [TV-MA] (6/10)

item.title: 7th Feb: Azali (2018), 1hr 29m [TV-MA] (6/10)

item.title: 7th Feb: The Ballad of Lefty Brown (2017), 1hr 51m [R] (6.1/10)

item.title: 7th Feb: Fifty: The Series (2018), 2 Seasons [TV-14] (6/10)

item.description: This documentary profiles a defiant driver who challenged racial barriers in American auto racing, becoming the first black man to race in the Indy 500.

item.title: 5th Feb: Arrow (2019), 8 Seasons [TV-14] - New Episodes (6/10)
item.description: [New Episodes] Based on DC Comics' Green Arrow, an affluent playboy becomes a vengeful superhero, saving the city from villains armed with just a bow and arrows.
